I"4<p>You can extend the estimated completion date of an opportunity if you need more time to complete the work.</p>

<p>To extend an opportunity:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Make sure the participants, home office, and host office agree to the extension.</li>
  <li>Sign in to Open Opportunities.</li>
  <li>Go to your <strong>Created Opportunities</strong> section,.</li>
  <li>Click the opportunity you want to extend.</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Edit</strong>.</li>
  <li>Change the <strong>Estimated completion date</strong>.</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</li>
</ol>
